*/

Interface pedInterfacepost
Public Method New()
Public Method getPedido() as Character
Public Method getItem() as Character
Public Method getQtdCan() as Numeric
Public Method getProd() as Character
Public Method setPedido(c)
Public Method setItem(c)
Public Method setQtdCan(n)
Public Method setProd(c)
EndInterface

Interface  pedInterfaceget
Public Method New()
Public Method getPed() as Character
Public Method getProd() as Character
Public Method getCNumQuery() as Character
Public Method getCQuant() as Character
Public Method setPed(c)
Public Method setProd(c)
Public Method setCNumQuery(c)
Public Method setCQuant(c)
Public Method dados() as Logical
EndInterface

Interface alteraInterface
Public Method New()
Public Method updateC6()
Public Method updateC5()
EndInterface

Interface ConsultarInterface
Public Method New()
Public Method consultar() as Logical
EndInterface

/*
/=========\
| CLASSES |
\=========/
*/

Class pedItenspost Implements pedInterfacepost
    Private data cPedido as Character
    Private data cItem as Character
    Private data cQtdCan as Numeric
    Private data cProd as Character
    Private data cStatus as Character
    Public Method New()
    Public Method getPedido() as Character
    Public Method getItem() as Character
    Public Method getQtdCan() as Numeric
    Public Method getProd() as Character
    Public Method getStatus() as Character
    Public Method setPedido(c)
    Public Method setItem(c)
    Public Method setQtdCan(n)
    Public Method setProd(c)
    Public Method setStatus(c)
EndClass

Class pedItensget Implements pedInterfaceget
    Private data cPed as Character
    Private data cProd as Character
    Private data cNumQuery as Character
    Private data cQuant as Character
    Public Method New()
    Public Method getPed() as Character
    Public Method getProd() as Character
    Public Method getCNumQuery() as Character
    Public Method getCQuant() as Character
    Public Method setPed(c)
    Public Method setProd(c)
    Public Method setCNumQuery(c)
    Public Method setCQuant(c)
    Public Method dados() as Logical
EndClass


Class Update From pedItenspost Implements alteraInterface
    Public Method New()

    @Post("api_pedido/updatec6")
    Public Method updateC6()

    @Post("api_pedido/updatec5")
    Public Method updateC5()

EndClass

Class Consultar From pedItensget Implements ConsultarInterface
    Public Method New()

    @Get("/api_pedido/consultar/:cped/:cprod/:cnumquery/:cquantidade")
    Public Method consultar() as Logical

EndClass

